_sText:
Made this to do something like that: https://developer.valvesoftware.com/wiki/Weapon_cubemap, to test cubemap better in the map like the resolution and visually, no just checking the awp scope.

When installed, open the game enter the mapa that you want to use and use these commands:
Make sure you're in a surface and with noclip off

  1.  exec create_weapon_cubemap   - To create the spheres 
  •  set_pos_1   - Change the position of the sphere to default
  •  set_pos_2   - Change the position of the sphere to lower
  •  set_pos_3   - Change the position of the sphere more to lower
  •  set_pos_4   -  Change the position of the sphere up your head
  •  set_type_1   -  Change the sphere style to 1   
  •  set_type_2   -  Change the sphere style to 2   ( set_pos... don't work )
  •  delete_weapon_cubemap   -  Delete spheres 
  •  give_weapon_cubemap   -  Give the spheres again  ( don't use twice )
